            Summary = "How to pay vendors by ACH from the Batches tab: assembling eligible Bank Transfer payments into a NACHA file, generating and downloading it, releasing the batch (segregation of duties), prenote batches, and importing the bank's ACH return / NOC file. Available when an administrator has turned on bank payments.",
            ContentType = TrainingContentType.Article,
